casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Diana Beth DENRICH.
No. D-3020.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 2, 2018.
Diana Beth Denrich, of Frederick, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
